<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
      .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
      .payment-alert { background: #ffebee; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .action-needed { color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= @order.shipping_name %>,</p>
        
        <div class="payment-alert">
          <p class="action-needed">Action Required: Payment Failed for Order #<%= @order.id %></p>
          <p>Unfortunately, we were unable to process your payment for the following order:</p>
          <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@order.total_amount, unit: "â‚¹") %></p>
          <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> <%= @order.payment_method&.titleize %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Order Details:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Order Number: #<%= @order.id %></li>
          <li>Order Date: <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
        </ul>

        <p>Common reasons for payment failure:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Insufficient funds</li>
          <li>Incorrect payment details</li>
          <li>Bank declined the transaction</li>
          <li>Network or technical issues</li>
        </ul>

        <p>What to do next:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Check your payment details</li>
          <li>Ensure sufficient funds are available</li>
          <li>Try the payment again</li>
          <li>Contact your bank if the issue persists</li>
        </ol>

        <p>If you need assistance or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>We appreciate your patience and understanding.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 